@Node "howto" "NewLookMenuPatch/How To Use NewLookMenuPatch"

  Sorry,  but  there's no installation script right now.  If you
can't  handle  manual  installations then you might as well stop
reading and delete NLMP now :^)

The steps to enlightnment...

1. Copy  the NewLookMenuPatch and  KickWBTitle programs  to your
   C:  directory.

2. Edit  your     S:Startup-Sequence.   call  C:NewLookMenuPatch
   directly  after setpatch.  call C:KickWBTitle directly before
   LoadWB.   KickWBTitle  just  calls  _LVOOpenWorkBench  to get
   things going :^)

3. Reboot :^)

@EndNode

